I am trying to add another key to my roles identity table, `DatabaseId`. ef keeps generating the key as `nullable`, I tried to enforce it with `DataAnnotations` using `[Required]` tag but its not working, what am I doing wrong here?
I followed this article as well, [Relationships, Navigation Properties, and Foreign Keys][1] but its not working in this case, 

These are my entities,

    public class PracticeDatabase
        {
            public PracticeDatabase()
            {
                UserDatabases = new Collection<UserDatabase>();
                PracticeOccupation = new Collection<PracticeOccupation>();
                ApplicationUserRole = new Collection<ApplicationRole>();
            }
            [DatabaseGenerated(DatabaseGeneratedOption.Identity)]
            public Guid Id { get; set; }
            [Required]
